### Upload attachment (entidade)
#### types: galery | cover

POST http://localhost:8787/attachments?type=cover
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="sample.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./tests/images/sample.jpg
--boundary123--

### Upload attachment (trilha) - capa
#### Substitua "1" pelo ID da trilha criada

POST http://localhost:8787/attachments?type=cover&trailId=1
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary123

--boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="trail-cover.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ./tests/images/sample.jpg
--boundary123--

